{"tid":579923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【場地單車世錦賽】捕捉賽意外撼工作人員 刁小娟受傷送院","createTime":"2018-03-04T05:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T05:09:43.000Z","uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd820744ac348359ea9b1e8b03c8c61f5151569","tid":579923,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"荷蘭世界場地單車錦標賽，香港代表刁小姐曾出戰女子捕捉賽，最後敬陪末座，昨日她參加女子全能賽（共四個項目），但在第一個賽的捕捉賽出現意外，在比賽途中有工作人員行近賽道執拾之前炒車的單車零件時，剛好遇上正全速比賽的刁小娟，二人撞個正著，該工作人員頭部受損，現仍留醫，刁小娟亦相繼送院，幸只是皮外傷，現已返回酒店。刁小娟在女子全能賽亦未能完成四個賽項。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180303/57900977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180303%2F57900977&d=nyc8i0%2Bs%2Fm%2BshqH4QY3fkaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cee47993\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180303%2F57900977&h=22d224af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180303/57900977</a>"}]}